lead_paragraph: This week's Masters always had the makings for being something extra special and it lived up to expectations on Thursday as reigning champion Jordan Spieth seized a two-shot lead after the opening round.

headline.print_headline: Masterful Spieth Moves Two Ahead at Augusta
